<body>
    
    <h2 style="text-align: center;"><ins>CSS Border</ins></h2>
    
    <p> When you write some text and you want text border around line.</p>
    
    <p> Use border property inside <mark>style </mark>attribute</p>
    
    <p> An example are below this line </p>
    
    <p style="border:2px solid Violet;"> this text have border with 2px and color is solid violet </p>
    
    <h2 style="text-align: center;"><ins>CSS Padding</ins></h2>
    
    <p style="border: 2px padding:30px;">this is some text with padding use</p>
    
    <h2 style="text-align: center;"><ins>CSS Margin</ins></h2>
    
    <p> Margin are used for containing space between outside the border</p>
    
    
    
